            . The prisoners were strangers to me; I knew Mason by sight, I had such plates as these, I sold none to them - My boy absconded the same day.</p>
               <p>MASON'S Defence. His boy asked me to carry them to Whitechapel.</p>
               <p>SANUFORD'S Defence. I was looking at the shop, and this boy got in conversation with me.</p>
